short_desc: Provides youth with basic health care and resources to improve their well being and success in school
description: Serving students at San Lorenzo High School, Arroyo High School, and Sunset High Schools. The San Lorenzo High School-Based Health Center provides medical care including reproductive health services, sports physicals, prevention and treatment of STIs, health education and behavioral health services. Over half of San Lorenzo High students take advantage of services available and many students continue to receive services up to the age of 21.
